snippet.textDisplay: @medicosis Perfectionalis - Someone has forgotten to add the number of corpses being cremated in Wuhan and a multitude of other cities throughout china, to the list of infected and deaths. There are reports that in wuhan alone, that the average crematorium has been experiencing a 200% increase in workload every 24hrs since Jan 22nd 2020, and there is no time to do official medical reports or autopsies, because workers are under enormous stress to clear the backlog of bodies being left in the streets. So these are not on official CCP figures, that are being relayed to the WHO, because apart from the corpses being double body bagged, there is nothing to say that they died of COVID-19 or a heart attack - we only know that they are processing 200% more bodies than normal.
